<plot>When the going gets tough, the tough eat Nachos! In the grand tradition of 70's cop movies, Jack Killeggy wants vengeance after his partner, Tonto Goldberg is murdered. But as the case gets more complicated he seeks help from Bobby Hornwood, a Hollywood private eye to the stars. These two do more than tango... they kick ass and take names! In his directorial debut, Josh Wenzel satirizes cop genre films, combining sharp wit with slapstick. Leisure suits, mustaches, and sausage... what more can you ask for?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?117683</url></doc>
